OL,3,CFamilies of the Kielland oil rig
OL,4,Cdisaster: 'We haven't forgot about
OL,5,Cthem'
OL,7,FRelatives of Cumbrians killed in
OL,8,FNorway's biggest ever industrial
OL,9,Fdisaster say they are still seeking
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,FThe families of the 22 Britains killed
OL,13,Fin the Kielland oil rig disaster, when
OL,14,Fa floating platform housing 212 people
OL,15,Fcapsized in the North Sea oilfields,
OL,16,Fhave met with lawyers to discuss their
OL,17,Fnext legal steps.
