OL,3,CFamilies of the Kielland oil rig
OL,4,Cdisaster: 'We haven't forgot about
OL,5,Cthem'
OL,7,FAlan Hunter, whose father was among
OL,8,Fthose killed, says the families are
OL,9,Fpushing for a new inquiry into the
OL,10,Fdisaster which killed 123 people in
OL,11,F1980.
OL,13,FMr Hunter, from Cleator Moor, lost his
OL,14,F34-year-old dad, Keith Hunter, who was
OL,15,Fone of six men from Cumbria to die in
OL,16,Fthe disaster.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Alan Hunter
OL,19,Fsaid: "Have them lads just been left
OL,20,Fand forgot about? My dad was never
OL,21,Ffound.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
