OL,3,CFamilies of the Kielland oil rig
OL,4,Cdisaster: 'We haven't forgot about
OL,5,Cthem'
OL,7,F"They forgot about them all. But we
OL,8,Fhaven't, we haven't forgot about them."
OL,10,FEarlier this year Mr Hunter travelled
OL,11,Fto Stavanger in Norway to mark the
OL,12,F44th anniversary of the tragedy. He
OL,13,Fmet with members of The Kielland
OL,14,FNetwork ` a group of survivors and
OL,15,Fbereaved family members - who continue
OL,16,Fto call for a new inquiry.
OL,18,FColin Lamb senior was one of the 123
OL,19,Fwho died when the Alexander Kielland
OL,20,FOil Rig capsized in the North Sea.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
