OL,4,Cdisaster: 'We haven't forgot about
OL,5,Cthem'
OL,7,FMr Lamb continued: "I wanted to learn
OL,8,Fmore about the truth and what actually
OL,9,Fhad gone wrong and meeting with the
OL,10,Ffamilies and talking about their loss
OL,11,Fof their fathers and whatever, you
OL,12,Fknow, brothers meeting them has made
OL,13,Fit easier and it's good like.
OL,15,F"When we had the meeting to get
OL,16,Ftogether in Stavanger 12 months ago.
OL,17,FAnd I just want to know what the truth
OL,18,Fis."
