OL,7,FThis week the Hunter family have
OL,8,Ffinally had their father's passport
OL,9,Freturned to them - after more than 44
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThe families say they continue to look
OL,13,Fto the Norwegian Government for
OL,14,Fanswers.
