OL,7,FA Norwegian report published in 2021
OL,8,Fconcluded that there was no basis for
OL,9,Fa new inquiry and the safety
OL,10,Frecommendations from it were followed
OL,11,Fup on, but accepted the original
OL,12,Finquiry had undermined trust and not
OL,13,Fexamined liability.
OL,15,FA Foreign Office spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"We provided support to the families
OL,17,Fof the British nationals involved and
OL,18,Fremain in contact with the Norwegian
OL,19,Fauthorities."
